title: The.Escapists.2-PLAZA
description:
Release Date :  08/2017                    Protection : Steam 
Discs        :  1                          Genre      : Indie 

The  Ultimate  Prison Sandbox  Risk it  all to  breakout  from  the 
toughest prisons in the world. Explore the biggest prisons yet, with 
multiple floors, roofs, vents and underground tunnels. Youll have to 
live by the prison rules, attending roll call, doing prison jobs and 
following strict routines all the while secretly  engineering  your 
bid for freedom
